{"tid":1429934,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"文宣要再進化呀！！！文略長","createTime":"2019-08-07T15:21:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T16:05:03.000Z","uid":67118,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f41c8c888e66c1cb39f9fb14738a2ffb65d236ba","tid":1429934,"uid":67118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T15:21:59.000Z","msg":"是咁的 我呢兩日行過連儂牆都發覺啲文宣停留左係5/8<br />\n啲資訊無更新少左人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 加埋啱啱睇左啲文宣嘅方向<br />\n所以開個post大家討論下 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">啱聽嘅俾個正皮 唔啱聽嘅都想大家留個comment</span><br />\n<br />\n網上版：<br />\n頭先睇到有post啲藍絲group係youtube到落廣告<br />\n可唔可推到我地都有人落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n片我覺得可以剪啲警暴/亂拉人/亂打人/警黑合作<br />\n條片遲下又可以用係民間記者會 <br />\n仲有好似以前連登廣告咁 唔一定要片<br />\n可以係相引人click入去<br />\n我知呢個要錢 要時間 方法上可以參考攬炒巴<br />\n<br />\n現實：<br />\n呢個急啲 我得一個人一日貼唔到幾多份<br />\n連儂牆要update 要整走窮嘅資訊貼返啲新嘅<br />\n可以開多三個Conner <br />\n通告Conner用嚟預告未來一段時間嘅抗爭活動<br />\n長老Conner用嚟出實體長輩圖 繼續洗腦<br />\nCctvb Conner用嚟推一啲cctvb嘅衰野"},{"pid":"5f29c5eb46e4fac4d7260de6e16ed7f485104934","tid":1429934,"uid":67118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T15:30:55.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"87c641decb7e58d69c687bdd6c4bf44a5e556849","tid":1429934,"uid":67118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T15:31:07.000Z","msg":"毒撚無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"038f93756d0e78333d90651ccfde7118a34b96c2","tid":1429934,"uid":67118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T15:31:18.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"9eed734b2e80890d72f344267befe2a4e4931bcf","tid":1429934,"uid":284042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T15:31:35.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"a693f80125050e3163983854d956981fe165c4e8","tid":1429934,"uid":67118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T15:31:40.000Z","msg":"10<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\